# Maven build output
**/target/
**/dependency-check-report.html

# Node.js
**/node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# Compiled class files
**/*.class

# Package files
**/*.jar
**/*.war
**/*.ear

# IntelliJ / Eclipse
.idea/
*.iml
.classpath
.project
.settings/
.vscode/

